name: sagemakermultilabeltextclassification
description: Multi label text classification using the fastText with SageMaker BlazingText. Model is trained on the public dataset of [10% of Stack Overflow Q&A dataset](https://medium.com/r/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kaggle.com%2Fstackoverflow%2Fstacksample).
